data.description: Welcome to this spacious 5-bedroom, 3 bath,  ranch style home in popular Harrison Heights subdivision. Beautiful open kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and wood flooring. Enjoy the convenience of main floor laundry. The spacious primary bath features double sinks, granite, walk-in tile shower and natural light. The sprawling finished basement features a rec room, 2 additional legal bedrooms, a large family room and an additional full bath. Enjoy family gatherings and entertaining on the patio in the fenced backyard. Huge 3 stall garage with additional storage! Call to schedule your privates showing today.
